  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The Virtues Project (TVP) inspires people of all cultures to live by our highest values, our virtues. Our Five Strategies offer ways to live out the virtues. If you employ these Strategies, you can experience a more authentic, meaningful life; you can learn to raise children of compassion and integrity; your teachers can create safe, caring, and high-performing learning communities; and as leaders you can encourage ethics in workplace and community. TVP has reached over 135 countries since 1991.</narrative>
